  "title": "chore(deps): update dependency wdio-dot-reporter to v0.0.9",
  "body": "<p>This Pull Request updates dependency <a href=\"https://github.com/webdriverio/wdio-dot-reporter\">wdio-dot-reporter</a> from <code>v0.0.8</code> to <code>v0.0.9</code></p>\n<h3 id=\"commits\">Commits</h3>\n<p><details><br />\n<summary>webdriverio/wdio-dot-reporter</summary></p>\n<h4 id=\"009\">0.0.9</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/webdriverio/wdio-dot-reporter/commit/d95eb2328063f764fd6f170b8f10654d146e839c\"><code>d95eb23</code></a> 0.0.9</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/webdriverio/wdio-dot-reporter/commit/e27b2a5c33a73badc6e1d235289ece6780a48aad\"><code>e27b2a5</code></a> chore(package): update sinon to version 3.2.0</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/webdriverio/wdio-dot-reporter/commit/3b04a80baf3c48f7c70f1cc1d5804f3c79c5a514\"><code>3b04a80</code></a> chore(package): update sinon to version 3.1.0</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/webdriverio/wdio-dot-reporter/commit/0018ebd6459bd16fb72cb9906d6d63b55d3988e9\"><code>0018ebd</code></a> chore(package): update eslint to version 4.4.0</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/webdriverio/wdio-dot-reporter/commit/2ec8ce0080b434e04d4b411e7ea65e75b8e267f2\"><code>2ec8ce0</code></a> chore(package): update sinon to version 3.0.0</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/webdriverio/wdio-dot-reporter/commit/00e122284a80d185d8adb3ca5b2c0c4ec34fa972\"><code>00e1222</code></a> chore(package): update mocha to version 3.5.0</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/webdriverio/wdio-dot-reporter/commit/9e3b4b9907444bf757f7709d6fe0b309da05995f\"><code>9e3b4b9</code></a> chore(package): update sinon to version 2.4.0</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/webdriverio/wdio-dot-reporter/commit/eec2c86d9ee7c7be3202482fccaed8ef363c5bbf\"><code>eec2c86</code></a> chore(package): update eslint to version 4.3.0</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/webdriverio/wdio-dot-reporter/commit/8494c48ddf9b1362866e7b65cb43890265fbd3c6\"><code>8494c48</code></a> chore(package): update eslint to version 4.2.0</li>\n